Notes: UWO made 11 of its first 13 shots from the field, including five three-point
baskets, to take a 28-14 lead with 9:03 left in first half...UWO's Kitzke has
13 of her 17 points in the first 10:57 of play...WC rallied to take 50-49 lead
with 7:38 left...Brenneman's free throws with two seconds left seal WC win.
Game.Officials: Blaine Hilgendorf,  Erin Rickard,  Ralph Sirmons
